    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm parting ways with this beauty, and she\u2019s in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super dependable for me and still drives like a total charm. It's perfect for road trips or just zipping around town comfortably. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
