    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-string S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit is paired with a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity has been addressed with a reinforced rear subframe, and the suspension retains its factory precision with refreshed bushings and dampers. The engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a recent shim-and-bucket valve adjustment. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the performance metrics remain sharp. It features staggered Style 67 wheels and a braking system with cross-drilled rotors for superior heat management during spirited sessions. A robust, enthusiast-maintained example of Bavarian engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Runs well. Regular maintenance performed. Minor cosmetic wear.",
