      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to own. This car is in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend getaways. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so while there might be a tiny bit of character from normal use, it still looks great and drives even better! It's the perfect balance of comfort and performance for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle. I\u2019d love for it to go to a great new home, so feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
