      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant, delivering linear torque through a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis maintains excellent lateral rigidity, supported by a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. This example has undergone an IMS bearing retrofit and a recent borescope inspection to ensure internal mechanical integrity. Braking performance is sharp thanks to four-piston Monoblock calipers and vented rotors. While the exterior displays minor road patina consistent with spirited use, the underbody aero remains intact, and the hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback expected of a rear-engine icon. A mechanically sound, driver-focused machine ready for the track or the open road.",
